          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Excellence",
            "image1": "shopify://shop_images/Icons_4ca737a8-c2c7-4503-8394-2e8464fdc839.png",
            "content1": "<p>Forged with <strong>3-layered VG10-level harder steel</strong>, the blade delivers superior sharpness, edge durability, and long-lasting cutting performance.</p>",
            "image2": "shopify://shop_images/Icons_1_3fd4b30f-650d-4d53-b1dc-762b4e3307c0.png",
            "content2": "<p>An <strong>anti-stick finish</strong> combined with an <strong>ergonomic grip</strong> ensures smooth food release, comfortable handling, and safe, efficient control.</p>",
            "image3": "shopify://shop_images/Icons_2_a361cc00-44f9-4c96-860d-af10d34d43b7.png",
            "content3": "<p><strong>Advanced vacuum heat-treatment </strong>enhances blade hardness, retention, and resili-ence, ensuring reliable perfor-mance in professional use.</p>"
