              "name": "t:names.accordion_dash_row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "What steel is in the Retro Series?",
                "content": "<p>The Retro Series uses 10Cr15CoMoV steel with Damascus cladding. The 10Cr15CoMoV core is a Chinese-developed alloy that matches VG10 in performance, with added cobalt for hardness and molybdenum for corrosion resistance. It's hardened to 60 HRC for excellent edge retention.</p>",
