            "accordion_row_seo1": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "t:names.accordion_dash_row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Is the Retro Series Damascus pattern genuine?",
                "content": "<p>Yes. The Damascus pattern on Retro Series knives is created through actual forge-welding of multiple steel layers, not cosmetic etching. Each blade has a unique pattern formed during the forging process. The layering also adds structural benefits, with softer outer layers absorbing impact while the hard core maintains the cutting edge.</p>",
