              "name": "t:names.accordion_dash_row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "What handle does the Retro Series have?",
                "content": "<p>The Retro Series features an ebony wood handle with a classic octagonal shape. The natural wood provides excellent grip, even when wet, and develops a beautiful patina over time. The octagonal profile prevents the knife from rolling on the counter and suits the pinch grip favoured by experienced cooks.</p>",
